org.chronos.chronodb.internal.api

Interface TransactionConfigurationInternal

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ChronoDBTransaction.Configuration
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MutableTransactionConfiguration
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultTransactionConfiguration

    public interface TransactionConfigurationInternal
extends ChronoDBTransaction.Configuration
    An extended version of ChronoDBTransaction.Configuration.

    This interface and its methods are for internal use only, are subject to change and are not considered to be part of the public API. Down-casting objects to internal interfaces may cause application code to become incompatible with future releases, and is therefore strongly discouraged.
